name: Abandoned city
description: Since the world-wide pandemic, people have vanished from the streets, and this made me think of the orange scene from "Blade Runner 2049," so I tried to re-create that scene here in Korea.  On a photo walk in the Korean city of Cheonan, I remembered a place that I'd been before and went there straight away. My decision was right and I was able to capture this scene. / Video resolution : 6,000 x 3,242 / Duration : 30 seconds / Video format : .mp4(H.264)
